{"word":"ἀγκύλη","slug":"ἀγκύλη","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀγκύλη</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἄγκος'><el>ἄγκος</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>a loop</i> or <i>noose</i> in a cord,<a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>the thong of a javelin</i>, by which it was hurled: <i>the javelin</i> itself, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b><i>a bow-string</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}